<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">This was already a problem in a world without LLMs. Reputation is the only human mechanism that mitigates this.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44368859&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44367084%2344368859" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
