<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">Technology is a catalyser. It has a knack of turning things from &quot;already a problem&quot; to &quot;now a catastrophe&quot;.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44370534&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44367084%2344370534" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
