<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">I would argue that, at least for me, gen AI helps me learn things much faster.<p>E.g., like I said, previously I would have been turned off from doing some projects because I wouldn&#x27;t have spent a ton of time dicking around with things that are just inefficient. Now I have gen AI create a starting point, and it&#x27;s very clear to me &quot;Ah, this is how I would use grid layout to get what I want&quot;. I can tweak things and it&#x27;s very clear to me how things are working.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44371691&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44367084%2344371691" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
